ResourceHeader.ResourceName: Interball Auroral Probe SKA-3 2-min Key Parameters
ResourceHeader.Description:
This set of Interball Auroral Probe 2-min key parameters contains spectra and anistropy of electrons within energy ranges of 20-40
keV from two time-of-flight detectors EM-1-1 and EM-1-2. The field of view of these detectors are directed oppositely and perpendicular to the satellite 
rotation axis.  See more information at http://www.iki.rssi.ru/interball/
